<title>USA: Bio-Vascular files for FDA okay for patch.</title>
<headline>Bio-Vascular files for FDA okay for patch.</headline>
<dateline>ST. PAUL, Minn. 1997-05-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>Bio-Vascular Inc said Thursday it filed for U.S. Food and Drug Administration clearance for its CV Peri-Guard Cardiovascular Patch.</p>
<p>The CV Peri-Guard is for use by cardiac surgeons as an intracardiac patch, including vessel repair, value repair and suture-line buttressing.</p>
<p>&quot;With FDA clearance for intracardiac indications, we will gain immediate access to a market estimated to be a $20 million worldwide opportunity annually,&quot; John Karcanes, Bio-Vascular chief executive, said in a statement.</p>
<p>Bio-Vascular provides specialty medical products.</p>
<p>((--Chicago newsdesk, 312-408-8787))</p>
